                        Compendium of Incantations, a collection of 249 <foreign xml:lang="Sa-Ltn">dhāraṇī</foreign> incantations themselves (Toh 846-1093), and a small group of 15 texts
                        (Toh 1094-1108) included at the end of the section as a whole by way of dedication and aspiration prayers.</p>
